00:23:02.290 --> 00:23:03.778
[LAUGHTER]

00:23:08.750 --> 00:23:11.720
HABEN GIRMA: Great question, RJ.

00:23:11.720 --> 00:23:15.670
So, Google has so many
products and services.

00:23:15.670 --> 00:23:18.540
It's unbelievable.

00:23:18.540 --> 00:23:26.330
And I mentioned chat computer
conversation applications.

00:23:26.330 --> 00:23:31.210
And I've been using
Google Chat, which

00:23:31.210 --> 00:23:33.920
I believe is now
