00:23:33.920 --> 00:23:37.530
for many, many, many years.

00:23:37.530 --> 00:23:41.450
And that has been an amazing way
to connect with people, since I

00:23:41.450 --> 00:23:42.810
can't really hear on the phone.

00:23:46.600 --> 00:23:48.870
A lot of people like
using it, even people

00:23:48.870 --> 00:23:51.836
without disabilities.

00:23:51.836 --> 00:23:54.690
But for me, it's
been an amazing way,

00:23:54.690 --> 00:23:57.760
and I know for other people
with disabilities, people

00:23:57.760 --> 00:24:01.316
with hearing loss, people
on the autism spectrum,

00:24:01.316 --> 00:24:04.430
it's facilitated so
many connections.

00:24:04.430 --> 00:24:07.310
And it has allowed
a lot of communities

00:24:07.310 --> 00:24:09.810
to grow, and connect.

00:24:09.810 --> 00:24:13.445
And then for your last question,
I happen to use an iPhone.

