00:24:49.740 --> 00:24:52.290
and I would love
to see improved,

00:24:52.290 --> 00:24:55.960
is audio captioning
for YouTube videos.

00:24:55.960 --> 00:25:01.020
The idea is fantastic of
having computers automatically

00:25:01.020 --> 00:25:02.810
caption videos.

00:25:02.810 --> 00:25:05.880
That creates so
